Create users
useradd -c "coment" -g [group] user
 
remove all about user including home 
userdel -r user

you can find groups at /etc/group 

add a group
groupadd group 

modify group 
groupmod newname oldname

remove group
groupdel groupname

details of the user password
chage -l username 

set password expire 
chage -E "yyyy-mm-dd" username 

inavtive user 
chage -I username 

send a message to expire password 
chage -W 3 username 

